headline: Is Kinder Morgan Still Attractive After Recent 25% Surge and Pipeline Expansion News?
summary: If you’re wondering what’s really happening with Kinder Morgan stock right now, you’re not alone. The company’s share price has been anything but boring lately. Just over the past month, Kinder Morgan climbed 5.3%. If you zoom out to the past year, that return jumps to an impressive 25.4%. Even more striking, Kinder Morgan has more than doubled over the past five years, up a whopping 200.3%. That sort of run naturally turns heads, whether you’re a long-term holder or a potential investor...
